sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Server
    participant AI as OpenAI

    User->>Server: Send question
    Server->>AI: Request answer
    Note over AI: Start generating
    AI-->>Server: "The" (first chunk)
    Server-->>User: "The" (show immediately)
    AI-->>Server: " weather" (second chunk)
    Server-->>User: "The weather" (update)
    AI-->>Server: " is nice" (last chunk)
    Server-->>User: "The weather is nice" (complete)
